hen, some universal rules of action=\r\n and \nreaction govern how this works. Under the push of one&#39;s own previous =\r\nkarmas, one \nis placed in situations that are conducive to certain desires,=\r\n actions and \nawareness. The current karmas in those situations may further=\r\n modify the \nmomentum of the push (reaction) from previous actions. Though =\r\none&#39;s current \ndesires, actions and awareness are actually the work of the =\r\nall pervading \nshakti, they are also one&#39;s work in a way. It depends on how=\r\n we look at it and \nhow we abstract it. Though Ganges water in a bucket, Ga=\r\nnges water in a small \ncup, Ganges water in a cup in hot weather and Ganges=\r\n water in a cup in freezing \nweather are all Ganges water, they are differe=\r\nnt too. One is more, one is less, \none is warm and one is icy. Similarly, t=\r\nhe work of all pervading shakti is\ndifferent when expressed through differe=\r\nnt vessels (people) in different \nsituations.\n\nAs long as one actually feel=\r\ns internally (despite what one may say or pretend \nexternally) that one&#39;s d=\r\nesires, actions and knowledge are one&#39;s own, one is \nperforming karmas and =\r\nis bound to receive their kaarmik reactions. Only when the\nrealization that=\r\n it is all the work of the all pervading shakti becomes full and \ncompletel=\r\ny internalized, does one become free from the cycle of actions and \nreactio=\r\nns. Until then, all pervading shakti acts through one to give appropriate \n=\r\nreactions to actions one thinks one is performing.\n\n* * *\n\nIn astrological =\r\nterms, horoscope is the sum total of previous karmas, whose \nfruits one wil=\r\nl have to face. They show the circumstances faced by one. They do \nnot and =\r\ncannot determine what actions one engages in, though certain actions are \nm=\r\nore likely in certain circumstances.\n\nDestiny is the sum total of the react=\r\nions to the actions committed by one&#39;s free \nwill. Today&#39;s actions of free =\r\nwill become destiny tomorrow (i.e. on a future \ndate or in a future life).\n=\r\n\nBest regards,\nNarasimha\n--------------------------------------------------=\r\n--------\nFree Jyotish Software, Free Jyotish MP3 Lessons, Free Jyotish text=\r\nbook,\nFree &quot;Do It Yourself&quot; ritual manuals for short Homam and Pitri Tarpan=\r\na:\nhttp://www.VedicAstrologer.org\nFilms that make a difference: http://Sara=\r\nswatiFilms.org\nSpirituality: http://groups.yahoo.com/group/vedic-wisdom\nJyo=\r\ntish writings: http://groups.yahoo.com/group/JyotishWritings\n--------------=\r\n--------------------------------------------\n\n---- hramalingam@... wr=\r\note: \n&gt; Samadi state is not like getting a degree by hardwork It comes to c=\r\nertain \n&gt;people by the Grace of GOD Till GOD or Soul decides to reveal the =\r\nSamadi state \n&gt;whatever one does it is based on past karmas only\n&gt; Ramanapa=\r\ntham\n&gt; Sent from my BlackBerry=C2=AE on Reliance Mobile, India&#39;s No. 1 Netw=\r\nork. Go for it!\n&gt; \n&gt; -----Original Message-----\n&gt; From: Narasimha PVR Rao &lt;=\r\npvr@...&gt;\n&gt; Sender: vedic-wisdom@yahoogroups.com\n&gt; Date: Wed, 13 Oct=\r\n 2010 14:10:44 \n&gt; To: &lt;vedic-astrology@yahoogroups.com&gt;; &lt;vedic-wisdom@yaho=\r\nogroups.com&gt;; \n&gt;&lt;JyotishGroup@yahoogroups.com&gt;\n&gt; Reply-To: vedic-wisdom@yah=\r\noogroups.com\n&gt; Subject: [vedic-wisdom] Re: what does PURITY Mean\n&gt; \n&gt; Namas=\r\nte,\n&gt; \n&gt; I will give my 2 cents of free-wheeling comments in this area.\n&gt; \n=\r\n&gt; * * *\n&gt; \n&gt; Rules may have exceptions, but they are meant for general guid=\r\nance.\n&gt; \n&gt; Ramakrishna Paramahamsa and his disciples such as Swami Adbhutan=\r\nanda, Swami \n&gt;Vivekananda etc ate fish and yet achieved samadhi of various =\r\ntypes. However, we \n&gt;cannot compare ourselves with special beings and we sh=\r\nould follow rules and \n&gt;austerities laid out in tradition. Tendulkar may sc=